{"tid":2150783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八月十號仲有兩單好重要嘅新聞㗎！！","createTime":"2020-08-11T05:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T11:18:21.000Z","uid":196671,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba2dd90cd0557860916763137ecfc1fae49cd34","tid":2150783,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"第三第四項可能唔係好多人發覺，但有重大意義，隨時可能為驅逐所有外國記者及剝奪市民法律代表權鋪路！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuTrzO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuTrzO1.png&h=05e8599f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDtvR19hm3h/?igshid=siltep7piegu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDtvR19hm3h%2F%3Figshid%3Dsiltep7piegu&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=97ed24e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDtvR19hm3h%2F%3Figshid%3Dsiltep7piegu&h=6b42bce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDtvR19hm3h/?igshid=siltep7piegu</a>"},{"pid":"c9eef4b0086cb182791b7da5fb2d33a83f5517e6","tid":2150783,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84ea9a7cdf0ac4ac62293273fa3cb798b2d9244","tid":2150783,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2547302/入境處傳設新國安部門審批敏感簽證\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2547302%2F%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%82%B3%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=020c8d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2547302/入境處傳設新國安部門審批敏感簽證</a><br />\n<br />\n《信報》報道：<br />\n<blockquote>報道稱，外國記者的簽證申請必須經由該6月底成立的新部門。入境處過去從未公開過這樣的部門，但該部門是負責延誤包括《紐約時報》和《華爾街日報》在內的一些外國媒體組織的簽證續簽。<br />\n<br />\n報道又舉例指出，如果一位編輯未有在第一次簽證申請中，提及其工作職責包括報道新聞，假如在未來發現該編輯在報道一場抗議活動，其簽證續期申請可能會被推遲或拒絕。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31249b75e6571af7dfad35812b7deac2bf5869a0","tid":2150783,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=372846027036949&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D372846027036949%26_rdr&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=ce428e6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=372846027036949&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n有線新聞報道：<br />\n<blockquote>反修例事件超過650人被控暴動，近日法援署以經驗不足為由，拒絕委派多名大律師作辯護，包括曾處理旺角暴動案的大律師。法援署表示是按既定機制，以受助人的利益為依歸。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有超過十名大律師都遇到類似情況，包括一名參與過旺角暴動案的大律師。法援署以經驗不足為由，拒絕委派處理反修例的暴動案件。法援署重申以受助人利益為依歸，承認曾拒絕受助人提名的大律師，原因包括表現欠佳、未符合經驗要求、時間未能配合等，指名冊上仍有大量富經驗的大律師可接辦。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"524354469ed5445f4027b34b8bc995b489b8be1a","tid":2150783,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"936b129793467b8e1f362f2f8f6cadbe9f6f70b3","tid":2150783,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"685cbb24042663c15c4388bd67b36fc2b9a48e97","tid":2150783,"uid":70342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b27e7607be90c14ea2086e839de9ac1e9956315","tid":2150783,"uid":94021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9510bca8e697d0949994d015cd689e16dd8573b5","tid":2150783,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/